Class WebCmsAssetMenuViewsConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object

public class WebCmsAssetMenuViewsConfiguration
extends Object
    Allows configuration of a WebCmsMenuItem items for a WebCmsAsset. Requires the asset to also have a single WebCmsAssetEndpoint.
